channel.title: Undecided Dagger name {First 3D attempt}
channel.description:
Hai there. This is my 1 hour attempt at a knife/dagger. Yes, As you can see I'm not the best modeler in the world. The 3d is a bit sketchy because it's my first attempt at 3d (Copying the model, Inverting it, Relifting ect) This was originally supposed to be for Counter-strike. Obviously wouldn't work out, I'm still working on it. (It's going to be included in my Counter-strike:Source map named Downfall) Here's some pictures: [IMG]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x34/luke_livez/first3dmodel.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x34/luke_livez/first3dmodel2.jpg[/img]
This is my first model so please go easy.
